---
title: Mild Thai Red Coconut Chicken with Udon Noodles & Lemon
description: Our mild Thai red curry paste is just the right balance of flavour and heat, so everyone in the family can enjoy it. Use it to whip up
this saucy noodle dish, with chicken, carrot and Asian greens, plus a squeeze of lemon juice for bursts of freshness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-red-coconut-chicken-noodles-3541f469.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/thai-red-coconut-chicken-noodles-610340fabef3a06c5707af19-24215dec.pdf
